headline: First Leveraged ETFs on MDB and LRCX Set to Trade Next Week
summary: Tradr ETFs, a provider of ETFs designed for sophisticated investors and professional traders, announced today that it expects to launch two first-to-market leveraged single-stock ETFs on MongoDB (Nasdaq: MDB) and Datadog Inc. (Nasdaq: LRCX) on Tuesday, August 19. This launch will grow Tradr's leveraged ETF lineup to 23 funds with 18 of those representing single-stock strategies.
